**Overview**

The SentinelOne integrations dashboard provides a visual summary of application activity across your environment. The Applications by Installation Time and Detection Time line charts reveal trends in installation and detection events over time. The Applications by Host OS pie chart shows the distribution of applications across operating systems. The Applications by Host Name bar chart identifies hosts with the highest number of detected applications, supporting focused analysis.
